  "notes": [
    "Mode 7 rendering: road below horizon is scanline-raycasted in world space",
    "Sprites (karts, shells, bananas, item boxes) are billboarded using depth-based scale",
    "Camera always follows player kart position and angle, tilted slightly down",
    "Offroad detection: sample grass/road by checking if world point is within track polygon",
    "Drift: activate by holding shift+turn at >drift_min_speed; boost charges during drift",
    "Item box collision: circular radius check in 2D world space (not screen space)"
